data.description: This spacious home features 6 bedrooms and 3 full baths!! Primary bedroom has its own bath and a walk-in closest. Large eat-in kitchen and living room on the main level and a HUGE den in the basement with a woodstove on a brick surround. Located on 3.89 acres with a wrap-around driveway. Enjoy the beautiful view from the front porch! Recent updates include fresh paint, new light fixtures, new back door, new garbage disposal, new well pump 2021, new water heater 2022. Ask agent for complete list of updates. All appliances convey. (One bedroom doesn't have a window). Seller is willing to provide an allowance to remove raised floor in upstairs living room with an acceptable offer.
